- Durin\rquote s Day & Dragon-lore allow for a fast access on the Emerald of Doriath and other nice items in your SB\par
- Try to kill Leucaruth at Home for fast access to King under the Mountain, but it could be vital to keep it in play as a protection as well; we some items (Deadly Dart) & Sated Beast even Smaug at Home is a piece of cake.\par
- Try to get No Stranger at this time on Returned Exiles, so you do not have to squat at several sites!\par
- do not forget Clad for War to get full item points for most of your items!\b\par
